1
00:00:27,333 --> 00:00:29,333
[BIRDS TWEETING]

2
00:00:33,041 --> 00:00:35,041
[INSECTS CHIRPING]

3
00:00:45,416 --> 00:00:48,876
- [DOOR OPENS]
- [BABY CRYING]

4
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:51,000
[LAUGHS]

5
00:00:51,083 --> 00:00:55,383
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

6
00:00:55,458 --> 00:00:58,538
She's here! She's here. [LAUGHS]

7
00:01:00,125 --> 00:01:03,915
- [SPEAKING TOGRUTI]
- [CROWD MURMURING]

8
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:06,670
[CHUCKLING]

9
00:01:06,750 --> 00:01:08,420
Yeah! Come, come, come, come.

10
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:11,000
[CRYING CONTINUES]

11
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:18,000
[VILLAGERS MURMURING]

12
00:01:28,750 --> 00:01:31,460
[BABY COOING]

13
00:02:04,375 --> 00:02:06,035
[COOS]

14
00:02:09,250 --> 00:02:10,540
Ahsoka.

15
00:02:42,583 --> 00:02:43,753
[DROID BEEPS]

16
00:02:48,708 --> 00:02:49,748
[DROID BEEPS]

17
00:02:51,666 --> 00:02:52,876
[GROANS]

18
00:02:54,083 --> 00:02:55,253
[COOS]

19
00:02:56,625 --> 00:02:58,125
[PARENT] Are you sure she's ready?

20
00:02:59,375 --> 00:03:01,785
Nak-il, it is custom.

21
00:03:01,875 --> 00:03:04,745
In old days. Old ways for the old.

22
00:03:04,833 --> 00:03:07,753
Not you, Pav-ti. Not yet.

23
00:03:07,833 --> 00:03:11,383
Don't make fun. You'll insult the spirits.

24
00:03:11,458 --> 00:03:12,628
The trees?

25
00:03:12,708 --> 00:03:13,958
Ancestors.

26
00:03:14,041 --> 00:03:16,671
All right then. I meant no offense.

27
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,960
[DOOR BEEPS]

28
00:03:24,041 --> 00:03:27,291
Good hunting, Pav-ti, my little Soka.

29
00:03:27,375 --> 00:03:29,825
[BABBLES]

30
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:48,250
[BARKING]

31
00:03:51,625 --> 00:03:54,415
Pav-ti, off on the hunt?

32
00:03:55,333 --> 00:03:57,883
Has it been more than a year already?

33
00:03:57,958 --> 00:03:59,458
It has, Gantika.

34
00:04:10,666 --> 00:04:11,666
Well then.

35
00:04:14,166 --> 00:04:15,626
For luck.

36
00:04:19,541 --> 00:04:22,711
[GANTIKA SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

37
00:04:22,791 --> 00:04:24,081
[COOING]

38
00:04:27,791 --> 00:04:31,211
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

39
00:04:32,458 --> 00:04:33,668
Thank you, Gantika.

40
00:04:47,083 --> 00:04:49,633
[BARKING]

41
00:05:12,166 --> 00:05:15,826
[BIRD WARBLES]

42
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,540
[CHITTERING]

43
00:05:23,333 --> 00:05:24,333
[COOS]

44
00:05:29,458 --> 00:05:30,668
[CHITTERS]

45
00:05:45,583 --> 00:05:49,713
Look, Ahsoka, everywhere there is life.

46
00:05:50,375 --> 00:05:52,745
Value it. Honor it.

47
00:05:52,833 --> 00:05:55,463
[COOING, BABBLING]

48
00:06:10,583 --> 00:06:13,083
[GIGGLES, COOS]

49
00:06:19,708 --> 00:06:22,288
[GIGGLING]

50
00:06:25,958 --> 00:06:28,628
- [BABBLING]
- Shh.

51
00:06:30,458 --> 00:06:32,958
[KYBUCK BRAYING]

52
00:06:49,291 --> 00:06:50,881
[BRAYING CONTINUES]

53
00:07:15,916 --> 00:07:17,666
[SNIFFS]

54
00:07:28,416 --> 00:07:29,576
[BLASTER FIRES]

55
00:07:29,666 --> 00:07:30,956
[BRAYING]

56
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:41,290
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

57
00:07:57,083 --> 00:08:00,253
[KYBUCK SNIFFS, GROANS]

58
00:08:00,916 --> 00:08:04,576
[LABORED BREATHING]

59
00:08:14,708 --> 00:08:18,168
[FUSSING]

60
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:25,208
You must face death, Ahsoka.
Do not fear it.

61
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:30,830
[LABORED BREATHING CONTINUES]

62
00:08:49,458 --> 00:08:54,248
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

63
00:09:14,333 --> 00:09:15,753
He's a heavy one.

64
00:09:16,375 --> 00:09:19,915
This one will feed many.
Think we can lift it?

65
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,830
[COOING]

66
00:09:21,916 --> 00:09:24,246
Yes. I think so too.

67
00:09:24,833 --> 00:09:27,793
- [GROWLING]
- We never take more than we need.

68
00:09:28,833 --> 00:09:33,923
I shall carry you and the kybuck,
unless you would like to carry him?

69
00:09:34,875 --> 00:09:36,995
[COOING]

70
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,080
[BABBLES]

71
00:09:46,250 --> 00:09:48,000
[COOING]

72
00:09:49,083 --> 00:09:51,673
[LOW GROWLING]

73
00:10:08,041 --> 00:10:09,631
[GROWLS]

74
00:10:15,625 --> 00:10:17,245
[ROARS]

75
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:18,833
[GROANS]

76
00:10:18,916 --> 00:10:21,166
[ROARING]

77
00:10:27,791 --> 00:10:29,001
- [GROWLS]
- [AHSOKA COOS]

78
00:10:30,958 --> 00:10:31,998
[ROARS]

79
00:10:36,333 --> 00:10:38,213
[PANTING]

80
00:10:38,291 --> 00:10:40,331
[BARKING]

81
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:41,416
[DROID BEEPS]

82
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:43,500
[BARKING CONTINUES]

83
00:10:43,583 --> 00:10:44,583
[DROID BEEPS]

84
00:10:45,375 --> 00:10:46,745
Pav-ti.

85
00:10:46,833 --> 00:10:48,633
[ROARING]

86
00:11:01,916 --> 00:11:05,746
[ROARING]

87
00:11:07,916 --> 00:11:09,376
[GIGGLING]

88
00:11:12,041 --> 00:11:13,421
[PAV-TI GRUNTS]

89
00:11:23,666 --> 00:11:27,786
- No! No! Ahsoka!
- [CRYING]

90
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:36,540
Ahsoka. [SOBBING]

91
00:11:36,625 --> 00:11:37,955
Ahsoka.

92
00:11:54,625 --> 00:11:57,035
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

93
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,380
[BABBLING]

94
00:12:42,208 --> 00:12:43,328
[SNEEZES]

95
00:12:43,416 --> 00:12:46,076
[GROWLS, ROARS]

96
00:12:46,166 --> 00:12:48,326
[COOING]

97
00:12:53,666 --> 00:12:56,576
[GROWLING]

98
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:27,713
[GROWLING]

99
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:40,080
I'm sorry, Nak-il.
There's no sign of her or the creature.

100
00:13:40,166 --> 00:13:43,826
We will go out in force.
We will not stop until we find her.

101
00:13:43,916 --> 00:13:46,706
[CREATURE GROWLING]

102
00:13:59,916 --> 00:14:01,416
[ROARS]

103
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:03,500
Wait.

104
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:35,290
[COOING]

105
00:14:59,708 --> 00:15:03,918
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

106
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:07,380
[SPEAKING TOGRUTI]

107
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:42,040
Gantika, how could this be?

108
00:15:49,625 --> 00:15:54,035
Jedi. Ahsoka is Jedi.

109
00:16:01,916 --> 00:16:04,036
[COOING]

